---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative mt-24 bg-[color:var(--color-primary)] text-white">
  <div class="container-x py-16 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white text-[color:var(--color-primary)] font-display">I</span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-lg leading-tight">IAM</p>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70">Infancia y Adolescencia Misioneras</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-md text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        Desde la infancia, misioneros de la vida. Movimiento que educa, acompaña y defiende
        la dignidad de cada vida humana desde la concepción.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60 mb-4">Navegación</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="#mision" class="hover:text-white/70">Misión</a></li>
        <li><a href="#problema" class="hover:text-white/70">El problema</a></li>
        <li><a href="#historias" class="hover:text-white/70">Historias</a></li>
        <li><a href="#ayudar" class="hover:text-white/70">Cómo ayudar</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60 mb-4">Contacto</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
        <li>contacto@iam.org</li>
        <li>+00 000 000 000</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 pt-2">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="hover:opacity-80">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook" class="hover:opacity-80">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="YouTube" class="hover:opacity-80">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="3"/><path d="M10 9l5 3-5 3z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-white/10">
    <div class="container-x py-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 justify-between items-center text-xs text-white/60">
      <p>© {year} IAM — Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <p>Hecho con esperanza por la vida.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
